data.description: Exclusive home offered for the first time, this custom log home and 34+ acres sit in a peaceful and private setting ,made of 6x12 solid pine logs this home offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, wood burning fireplace/ gas log conversion, covered porches, finished/heated 2-car garage, guest quarters/in-law apartment with additional full bath and kitchenette with separate entrance, spring fed pond stocked with bass, bluegill and crappie and full basement (heated/cooled & not included in square footage)! This meticulously cared for property takes in views of Savage Gulf and perfect for the hiker, hunter and outdoor enthusiast! Located near ISHA , Fall Creek Falls State Park and centrally located in Middle TN!           BY APPOINTMENT ONLY
